data.title: The Aristocats (Special Edition) (DVD)
data.meta_description: Shop The Aristocats (Special Edition) (DVD) at Target. Choose from Same Day Delivery, Drive Up or Order Pickup. Free standard shipping with $35 orders.
data.text: Celebrating the 25th anniversary of its original release in December 1970, will be available for the first time ever on video. This animated masterpiece features a wealth of purebred voices including Phil Harrris, Eva Gabor, and Sterling Holloway.
